              Share <i class="bi bi-share-fill ms-2"></i>
            </button>
          </div>

        </div>
        <div class="w-100 ratio ratio-16x9" id="eventVideo">
          <iframe src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/Wm02nVcCuLw?si=vP-YRy_2oGUO6xO1" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe>
        </div>

        <div class="my-2 text-muted" id="eventVideoCaption">
          See more <a href="#">livestreams of previous events here.</a>
        </div>

        <section class="my-2">
          <h2>Overview</h2>
          <p>
            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Vel fugit veniam eum, cum voluptatem porro reiciendis, labore quisquam perspiciatis maxime quibusdam molestiae ipsa mollitia perferendis distinctio quod. Quibusdam, perferendis quo?
            <br>
            <a class="mt-2" href="#">More Details...</a>
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="my-2">
          <h2>Location</h2>
          <p>
            Description of where the event will be taking place including the full street address of the location and any additional instructions if the location is hard to find.
          </p>

          <div class="d-flex w-100 justify-content-center m-3" id="eventMap">
            <div class="w-75 ratio ratio-4x3">
              <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d6110.836363565991!2d-4.151417445552584!3d50.365115243145716!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x486c93523513aff1%3A0x6b15fe0380665f2a!2sThe%20Hoe%2C%20Plymouth!5e1!3m2!1sen!2suk!4v1744554437001!5m2!1sen!2suk" style="border:0;" allowfullscreen="" loading="lazy" referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"></iframe>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="my-2">
          <h2>Time</h2>
          <p>
            The event will be held on 
            <a href="https://calendar.google.com/calendar/render?action=TEMPLATE&text=Bonfire%20Night%202025&dates=20251111T180000Z/20251111T200000Z&details=%3Cp%3ERemember%2C%20remember%20the%20fifth%20of%20November!%26nbsp%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGet%20ready%20for%20an%20unforgettable%20night%20of%20fun%20and%20fireworks%20as%20Plymouth%20Hoe%20comes%20alive%20on%20Wednesday%205%20November%26nbsp%3Bfor%20Bonfire%20Night!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMake%20your%20way%20to%20the%20iconic%20Smeaton%E2%80%99s%20Tower%20lighthouse%20for%20the%20best%20views%20of%20the%20bonfire%2C%20which%20will%20be%20lit%20at%207pm.%20Feel%20the%20warmth%20of%20the%20roaring%20flames%20as%20you%20gather%20around%20with%20friends%20and%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20at%207.30pm%2C%20prepare%20to%20be%20wowed!%20The%20skies%20will%20explode%20with%20a%20stunning%20fireworks%20display%20launched%20from%20the%20historic%20Royal%20Citadel.%20Expect%20an%20incredible%20show%20of%20rockets%2C%20fountains%2C%20and%20crackling%20firecrackers%20lighting%20up%20the%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20fun%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20start%20there!%20From%204pm%2C%20Plymouth%20Hoe%20will%20be%20transformed%20into%20a%20buzzing%20hub%20of%20entertainment.%20With%20thrilling%20rides%20for%20all%20ages%20and%20a%20special%20children's%20fairground%2C%20there's%20something%20for%20everyone.%20Plus%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20miss%20out%20on%20the%20food%20and%20drink%20stalls%20opening%20from%205pm%20to%20keep%20you%20fuelled%20throughout%20the%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20the%20perfect%20event%20for%20the%20whole%20family%2C%20so%26nbsp%3Bwrap%20up%20warm%2C%20soak%20in%20the%20excitement%2C%20and%20enjoy%20an%20evening%20to%20remember!%3C%2Fp%3E&location=%20The%20Hoe%2C%20Plymouth%2C%20Devon%2C%20PL1%202PA&ctz=UTC">
              November 11th 2025 from 6pm to 7pm.
            </a>
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="my-2">
          <h2>Price</h2>
          <table class="table table-striped table-hover w-25">
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th style="width: 8ch;" scope="col">Person</td>
                <th style="width: 1em;"></th>
                <th style="width: 8ch;" scope="col">Price</td>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td>Adult</td>
                <td></td>
                <td>£2.99</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                  <td>Student</td>
                  <td>
                    <a href="" onclick="return false;" 
                      data-bs-toggle="popover" data-bs-trigger="hover" 
                      data-bs-content="Anyone currently enrolled on a undergraduate or postgraduate course at a university. Must be in possession of student ID.">
                      <i class="bi-info-circle-fill h4 mx-5"></i>
                    </a>
                  </td>
                  <td>£2.50</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Child</td>
                <td>
                  <a href="" onclick="return false;" 
                    data-bs-toggle="popover" data-bs-trigger="hover" 
                    data-bs-content="Anyone under the age of 16.">
                    <i class="bi-info-circle-fill h4 mx-5"></i>
                  </a>
